\b nox is a framework\

\b0 it does everything mentioned above. but it does not do\
a lot of other things. amongst others:\
\

\b nox does not render anything\
i
\b0 t is not about representation. it does come bundled with a \
render engine that is sufficient to build a website. other\
render engines may be added manually.\
\

\b nox does not manage anything\
i
\b0 t is not about content management. it does come bundled with a \
simple cms that allows you to manage services, nodes, users and\
relations. other cmses may be added manually.\
